
			 ===============
  		  	     pyscript
  			 ===============
  

--------------------------------------------------------------------
 Summary
--------------------------------------------------------------------

Pyscript is a set of modules and scripts for python that facilitate
the creation of high-quality postscript diagrams. The diagrams are
scripted rather than drawn.

See http://pyscript.sourceforge.net


--------------------------------------------------------------------
 Instalation
--------------------------------------------------------------------

copy the subdirectory "pyscript" (the one with __init__.py in it) to
somewhere on your python search path,

eg $cp -a pyscript /usr/lib/python2.1/site-packages/

now pyscript should by available from within python by
>> from pyscript import *


